Tim Burton is rumored to have hooked up with Eva Green in Dec 2015.

About

Tim Burton is a 65 year old American Film Director. Born Timothy William Burton on 25th August, 1958 in Burbank, California, he is famous for Director of the films "Batman" (1989), "Edward Scissorhands", "The Nightmare Before Christmas", "Sweeney Todd: The Demon Barber of Fleet Street in a career that spans 1979–present and 1971–present. His zodiac sign is Virgo.

Eva Green is a 43 year old French Actress. Born Eva Gaëlle Green on 6th July, 1980 in Paris, Ile de France, France, she is famous for her roles as Sibylla, Princess of Jerusalem in the epic historical fiction drama film Kingdom of Heaven (2005), Vesper Lynd in the spy film Casino Royale (2006), Angelique Bouchard in the epic mystery dark fantasy black comedy film Dark Shadows (2012), Miss Alma Peregrine in the fantasy film Miss Peregrine’s Home for Peculiar Children (2016), Artemisia in the epic action film 300: Rise of an Empire (2014), Eve Connors in the art drama thriller film White Bird in a Blizzard (2014), Sarah in the drama film Proxima (2019), Vanessa Ives in the Showtime horror drama series Penny Dreadful, Morgan Pendragon in the Starz fantasy historical drama series Camelot, and Lydia Wells in the TVNZ/BBC drama series The Luminaries in a career that spans 2001–present and 2001–present. Her zodiac sign is Cancer.
